'''Anna''' is Pru's part-time nanny.

==History==
Anna brought Pru to the station in order to hand her over to Ben. When she arrived, she ended up flirting with Jack while she waited for Ben. When Ben asked who she was, she explained that the Millers had been struggling with Pru, so they asked her to step in part-time. ''("[[The Little Things You Do Together]]")''

Anna later brought Pru to Ben and Bailey's when Ifeya and Bill were delayed by a medical appointment. ''("[[Cold Blue Steel and Sweet Fire]]")''

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
While dropping off Pru, she flirted with [[Jack Gibson]].

===Friendships===
She went to school with [[Yemi Miller]], which is how she knows the Miller family.

==Career==
She works part-time as a nanny for [[Pruitt Arike Miller]].

==Notes and Trivia==
*She's in a band.<ref>[[The Little Things You Do Together]], 5x11 (S19)</ref>
